reviewText: Loved!!!! This chair video. I am a teacher and sometimes just want to have someone queue me. Great queues! I would highly recommend!!

I liked the whole body workout.  There are 3 workouts, and I usually do one a day.  Each is less than 1/2 an hour, and then I get the variety.  I hope she does more.  Not too fancy, but like training with an instructor in my livingroom.
